{{main|1941年德克萨斯飓风}}
本季的第一个风暴消散几天后，一股热带低气压于9月17日在[[尤卡坦半岛|尤卡坦半岛]]以北约190公里的墨西哥湾中部形成。形成后系统开始总体朝北移动<ref name="HURDAT" />，到了9月18日清晨，系统在路易斯安那州[[新奥尔良|新奥尔良]]东南偏南方向超过480公里外发展成热带风暴。之后的三天时间里，风暴朝东南偏南作顺时针方向移动，之后再转朝西面前进。9月21日系统增强为一级飓风后，风暴可能开始以一个更偏西北方向的路径朝[[美国墨西哥湾沿岸地区|德克萨斯湾沿岸]]逼近，于9月23日下午达到每小时201公里的最高风速。约4小时后（协调世界时9月23日22点左右），风暴在[[马塔哥达县|马塔哥达县]][[县城|县城]]{{link-en|贝城 (德克萨斯州)|Bay City, Texas|贝城}}东部登陆。估计其中心最低气压低至942[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡_(单位)|百帕]]，27.8[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）<ref name="US hurricanes">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | author3 = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | title = Chronological List of All Continental United States Hurricanes: 1851–2012 | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's Office of Oceanic & Atmospheric Research | date = 2013-07 | accessdate = 2013-11-27 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html | archivedate = 2013-11-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131104155015/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html }}</ref>。系统接下来蜿蜒朝东北方向前进，与[[休斯顿|休斯顿]]东部擦身而过，然后继续加速朝内陆进发。风暴于9月25日转变为一股[[温带气旋|温带风暴]]，最后一次纪录是于协调世界时9月27日0点在[[魁北克|魁北克]]东北上空，接近[[通戈山国家公园|通戈山国家公园]]<ref name="MWR" /><ref name="HURDAT" />。

许多地区都针对风暴发布了警告和预警，约25000人从自己家中撤离<ref name="MWR" />。官员采取了多项预防措施<ref>{{cite news | title = Hurricane Poised to Hit Texas | date = 1941-09-23 | work = The Evening Independent | accessdate = 2013-11-27 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=a6kLAAAAIBAJ&sjid=KVUDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6415,5231439 | archive-date = 2016-05-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160501111500/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=a6kLAAAAIBAJ&sjid=KVUDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6415,5231439 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。沿海岸地区的阵风风速达到每小时160公里<ref>{{cite web | title = Houston, Tex., Feels Lash of Coastal Storm | date = 1941-09-24 | work = The Chicago Daily Tribune | accessdate = 2013-11-27 | archivedate = 2018-01-01 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180101191203/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/chicagotribune/doc/176636369.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:AI&type=historic&date=&author=&pub=&edition=&startpage=&desc= | url = http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/chicagotribune/doc/176636369.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:AI&type=historic&date=&author=&pub=&edition=&startpage=&desc= }}</ref>，并纪录到很高的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]<ref name="MWR" />。飓风造成了严重的灾害，毁坏财产价值估计有200万美元（1941年美元，相当于{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|2000000|1941}}}}{{#time:Y}}年美元），此外农作物还受到了约500万美元（1941年美元，相当于{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|5000000|1941}}}}{{#time:Y}}年美元）的损失，其中以[[水稻|水稻]]和[[棉花|棉花]]为主。风暴共计造成四人死亡<ref name="MWR" />。飓风还影响了路易斯安那州的南部地区，这里一星期后将举行路易斯安那演习。暴雨引发了洪水和河水泛滥，导致军队车辆陷在泥中<ref>{{cite web |author=Velmer Lenora Smith |title=World War II — Louisiana Maneuvers |publisher=Beauregard Parish Library |accessdate=2013-11-27 |url=http://www.beau.org/~velmer/local/ww2.html |archivedate=2013-11-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131101185453/http://www.beau.org/~velmer/local/ww2.html }}</ref>。恶劣的天气还迫使数百架军用飞机飞向内陆暂时躲避<ref name="headed">{{cite news | title = Gulf Storm Is Headed For Texas | date = 1941-09-22 | work = The Evening Independent | accessdate = 2013-11-27 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=aqkLAAAAIBAJ&sjid=KVUDAAAAIBAJ&pg=3460,5129833 | archive-date = 2016-05-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160521053035/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=aqkLAAAAIBAJ&sjid=KVUDAAAAIBAJ&pg=3460,5129833 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

